[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Context    │ Comment Styles                                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ───────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────────────          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Shell      │ # (to EOL), : 'comment' (noop colon)                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Concatenation Methods for Shell                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
